#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.homepage
msgid ""
"<span class=\"base-fs\">Planning a wedding, birthday, or corporate event?"
"&amp;nbsp;<br/>Let BloomWorks create breathtaking floral decor tailored to "
"your vision. From elegant bridal bouquets to stunning centerpieces and venue "
"designs, we’ll make your event bloom with beauty.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"base-fs\">Načrtujete poroko, rojstni dan ali poslovni dogodek?"
"&amp;nbsp;<br/>Naj BloomWorks ustvari osupljivo cvetlično dekoracijo, "
"prilagojeno vaši viziji. Od elegantnih poročnih šopkov do osupljivih "
"osrednjih okraskov in oblikovanja prizorišča, poskrbeli bomo, da bo vaš "
"dogodek zacvetel z lepoto.</span>"

