#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>\n"
"                    <font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">The Point of "
"Sale app </font><font class=\"text-o-color-5\"><span style=\"font-weight: "
"normal;\">h</span></font>\n"
"                </strong>\n"
"                andles in-store sales of bouquets, flowers, gift cards, and "
"more."
msgstr ""
"<strong>\n"
"                    <font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">Aplikacija "
"Prodajno mesto </font><font class=\"text-o-color-5\"><span style=\"font-"
"weight: normal;\">h</span></font>\n"
"                </strong>\n"
"                prodaja sveč v trgovini, šopkov, rož, darilnih bonov in še "
"več."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>\n"
"                    <font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">The Sales app "
"</font>\n"
"                    <font class=\"text-o-color-5\"><span style=\"font-"
"weight: normal;\">makes it simple to handle customer orders, including big "
"floral arrangements for weddings, corporate events, and other special "
"occasions.</span></font>\n"
"                </strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>\n"
"                    <font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">Aplikacija "
"Prodaja</font>\n"
"                    <font class=\"text-o-color-5\"><span style=\"font-"
"weight: normal;\">olajša obdelavo naročil strank, vključno z velikimi "
"cvetličnimi aranžmaji za poroke, poslovne dogodke in druge posebne "
"priložnosti.</span></font>\n"
"                </strong>"

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">The CRM app</font></"
"strong><font class=\"text-o-color-5\"> helps you manage customer "
"relationships, event requests, and flower inquiries easily.</font><br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">Aplikacija CRM</font></"
"strong><font class=\"text-o-color-5\"> vam pomaga enostavno upravljati "
"odnose s strankami, zahteve za dogodke in povpraševanja po cvetju.</font><br/"
">"

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">The Purchase app</font></"
"strong> manages vendor and ensures your shop is stocked with the freshest "
"flowers."
msgstr ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">Aplikacija Nakup</font></"
"strong> upravlja s prodajalci in zagotavlja, da je vaša trgovina založena z "
"najsvežjim cvetjem."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">The Website app </font></"
"strong>allows customers to showcase your flowers vision and services online."
msgstr ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">Aplikacija Spletna stran </"
"font></strong>strankam omogoča, da na spletu predstavijo vašo vizijo in "
"storitve cvetja."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.contactus
msgid ""
"<strong><strong><i class=\"fa fa-phone fa-fw\"/></strong></strong>&amp;nbsp;"
"+44 1223 123456"
msgstr ""
"<strong><strong><i class=\"fa fa-phone fa-fw\"/></strong></strong>&amp;nbsp;"
"+386 41 123456"

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Activate payment methods: </strong>Activate payment options such as "
"Cash, Card, Mobile Payments, and Gift Cards directly in your POS settings."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Aktivirajte načine plačila: </strong>Aktivirajte možnosti plačila, "
"kot so gotovina, kartica, mobilna plačila in darilne kartice, neposredno v "
"nastavitvah vašega POS terminala."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Basics</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Osnove</strong>"

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Choose the best deal</strong>: Pick the vendor offering the best "
"deal for the requested materials."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Izberite najboljšo ponudbo</strong>: Izberite prodajalca, ki ponuja "
"najboljšo ponudbo za zahtevane materiale."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Create a Purchase Order</strong>: Order the flowers, plants, and "
"accessories you need for your business."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Ustvari naročilnico</strong>: Naročite rože, rastline in dodatke, ki "
"jih potrebujete za svoje podjetje."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Create tailored sales quotations: </strong>Generate a customized "
"Sales Quotation for weddings, birthdays, or corporate floral events, "
"directly on the sales app."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Ustvarite prilagojene prodajne ponudbe: </strong>Ustvarite "
"prilagojeno prodajno ponudbo za poroke, rojstne dneve ali korporativne "
"cvetlične dogodke, neposredno v prodajni aplikaciji."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Extend your offerings: </strong>Configure Gift Cards to offer "
"flexible floral gifts and provide more options for your clients."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Razširite svojo ponudbo: </strong>Konfigurirajte darilne kartice, da "
"ponudite prilagodljiva cvetlična darila in svojim strankam zagotovite več "
"možnosti."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Manage customer requests</strong>: Track customer inquiries coming "
"from your Website (such as wedding floral requests or custom bouquet "
"orders), manage engagement, follow up easily, and convert them into "
"confirmed sales\n"
"            opportunities."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Manage customer requests</strong>: Spremljajte povpraševanja strank, "
"ki prihajajo z vašega spletnega mesta (kot so zahteve za poročno cvetje ali "
"naročila šopkov po meri), upravljajte angažiranost, preprosto spremljajte in "
"jih pretvorite v potrjene prodajne\n"
"            priložnosti."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Organize event projects: </strong>Create a project to manage and "
"organize specific events, assign tasks, set deadlines, and track progress."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Organizirajte projekte dogodkov: </strong>Ustvarite projekt za "
"upravljanje in organizacijo določenih dogodkov, dodeljevanje nalog, "
"določanje rokov in spremljanje napredka."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Set up product offering: </strong>Create and configure your flower "
"products and add variants if you have different size or color for the same "
"product. You can also add an extra charges for specific options (e.g., +£2 "
"for a\n"
"            red tulip, +£10 for a medium bouquet)."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Nastavite ponudbo izdelkov: </strong>Ustvarite in konfigurirajte "
"svoje cvetlične izdelke ter dodajte različice, če imate za isti izdelek "
"različne velikosti ali barve. Za določene možnosti lahko dodate tudi "
"doplačilo (npr. +2 € za rdeč tulipan, +10 € za srednje velik šopek)."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Showcase your floral vision and offer: </strong>Configure your "
"website to highlight your floral style, present your services and get new "
"opportunities through a contact form."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Predstavite svojo cvetlično vizijo in ponudbo:</"
"strong>Konfigurirajte svojo spletno stran tako, da poudari vaš cvetlični "
"slog, predstavi svoje storitve in pridobi nove priložnosti prek kontaktnega "
"obrazca."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Take orders in Point of Sale</strong>: Open a register and process "
"in-store purchases such as bouquets, flowers, cards, and more."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Sprejemanje naročil na prodajnem mestu</strong>: Odprite blagajno in "
"obdelajte nakupe v trgovini, kot so šopki, rože, voščilnice in drugo."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Use Case</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Primer uporabe</strong>"

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>You didn't import demo data?</strong> You can still do it. Go to "
"<strong>Apps &gt; Industries &gt; Upgrade your Florist Package</strong> and "
"check the related box."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Nisi uvozil demo podatkov?</strong> Še vedno lahko to storiš. Pojdi "
"na <strong>Aplikacije &gt; Industrije &gt; Nadgradite svoj cvetličarski "
"paket</strong>in označite ustrezno polje."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Add the <strong>eCommerce </strong>features to extend your floral business."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte funkcije <strong>e-trgovine </strong>, da razširite svoje "
"cvetličarsko poslovanje."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Add<strong> product categories</strong> to organize your point of sales and "
"make your products easier to find during busy periods. (e.g. Bouquets, "
"Flowers, Plants, Other,...)"
msgstr ""
"Dodajte<strong> kategorije izdelkov</strong> , da organizirate prodajno "
"mesto in olajšate iskanje izdelkov v času največjega povpraševanja. (npr. "
"šopki, rože, rastline, drugo, ...)"

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Also, create beautiful <strong>Quotation Templates</strong> for specific "
"requests like wedding floral packages, making it faster and easier to send "
"offers to clients."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarite tudi čudovite <strong>Predloge Ponudb</strong> za posebne zahteve, "
"kot so paketi poročnega cvetja, s čimer boste hitreje in lažje pošiljali "
"ponudbe strankam."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid "Because: we can buy ourselves flowers! 💐"
msgstr "Ker: rože si lahko kupimo!💐"

