#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The package includes the Point of Sale (POS) app for handling in-store "
"purchases, the Sales app for managing quotations and orders, the Website to "
"showcase your floral vision and the Project app to track tasks and deadlines "
"for specific\n"
"        event requests. Whether you're creating a seasonal bouquet for a "
"gift or planning floral arrangements for a wedding, Odoo helps you stay "
"organized and deliver beautiful results to your clients."
msgstr ""
"Paket vključuje aplikacijo POS (Prodajno mesto) za upravljanje nakupov v "
"trgovini, aplikacijo Sales za upravljanje ponudb in naročil, spletno mesto "
"za predstavitev vaše cvetlične vizije in aplikacijo Projekt za sledenje "
"nalogam in rokom za posebne\n"
"        zahteve za dogodke. Ne glede na to, ali ustvarjate sezonski šopek za "
"darilo ali načrtujete cvetlične aranžmaje za poroko, vam Odoo pomaga ostati "
"organiziran in svojim strankam zagotoviti čudovite rezultate."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"There are millions of other ways to adapt your Odoo setup to fit your "
"business needs."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja na milijone drugih načinov, kako prilagoditi svojo Odoo nastavitev "
"svojim poslovnim potrebam."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"These all go free in your current subscription; feel free to explore! 🙃"
msgstr "Vse to je brezplačno v vaši trenutni naročnini; kar raziščite! 🙃"

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This setup is perfect for florists who specialize in providing fresh "
"flowers, customized bouquets, and event floral designs, catering to walk-in "
"customers and fulfilling orders for occasions like weddings, birthday "
"dinners, or corporate\n"
"        events."
msgstr ""
"Ta postavitev je idealna za cvetličarje, ki so specializirani za "
"zagotavljanje svežega cvetja, šopkov po meri in cvetličnih aranžmajev za "
"dogodke, za strežbo strank brez naročila in izpolnjevanje naročil za "
"priložnosti, kot so poroke, rojstnodnevne večerje ali poslovni\n"
"        dogodki."

#. module: florist
#: model:project.task.type,name:florist.project_task_type_1
msgid "To Do"
msgstr "Opravek"

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Track stock in real-time, manage multiple storage locations, automate "
"restocking, and monitor flowers freshness and avoid shortages with the "
"<strong>Inventory App</strong>."
msgstr ""
"Spremljajte zaloge v realnem času, upravljajte več skladiščnih lokacij, "
"avtomatizirajte ponovno polnjenje zalog, spremljajte svežino cvetja in se "
"izognite pomanjkanju z <strong>Aplikacijo Inventar</strong>."

#. module: florist
#: model:product.template,name:florist.product_template_7
msgid "Tulips"
msgstr "Tulipani"

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong>Planning App</strong> to schedule your team’s shifts, "
"ensuring the right staffing for busy event days."
msgstr ""
"Z <strong>Aplikacijo za Planiranje</strong> lahko načrtujete izmene svoje "
"ekipe in si zagotovite pravo osebje za dneve z veliko gneče na dogodkih."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong>Sales Reporting</strong> to analyze flower sales trends "
"around major events like Valentine's Day, Mother's Day, Father's Day, or "
"during summer wedding seasons."
msgstr ""
"S <strong>Poročili o Prodaji</strong> analizirajte trende prodaje cvetja "
"okoli večjih dogodkov, kot so valentinovo, materinski dan, očetovski dan ali "
"med poletno poročno sezono."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the chatter of a Purchase Order to communicate with the vendor about a "
"specific delivery and post a picture if something is missing compared to "
"what was ordered."
msgstr ""
"Za komunikacijo s prodajalcem o določeni dostavi uporabite klepet "
"naročilnice in objavite sliko, če kaj manjka v primerjavi z naročilom."

